name: Non Fungible Cards collection 16 - I own this peace of art
description: And I can prove it! Just look at my token, it registers all the journey of this card and now it belongs to me. I'm the happy owner of one of these two extremely rare items. And I bought it in the year of 2021, you weren’t even born at that time. Yeah, you can have a picture of this, I made a copy for you. But it'll not be the same. No, it's not about the image, it's about the code, man. You don't own the code. I own it. It 's mine! Only I have this code… well, me and another person.
